---
title: Double Slow-Cooked Irish Beef Stew with Potato Mash & Veggies
description: If you’re in the mood for a celebration feast without all the fuss or dishes, we suggest baking succulent slow-cooked beef and veggies. What Irish delight would be complete though without a serving of potatoes? Make it into a mash and those rich stew flavours will soak in and leave you feeling happy and warm.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6582537734da163846f08baa-9c57e628.jpeg
